<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA14">
<l>cāyāṟ kariyāṉai yuḷḷaṟiyā rāyneñcē</l>
<l>pēyār mulaikoṭuttār pēyarāy nīyārpōyt</l>
<l>tēmpūṇ cuvaittū ṉaṟintaṟintun tīviṉaiyām</l>
<l>pāmpārvāyk kainīṭṭaṟ pārttu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being one who on the inside does not know by complexion the Black one, o heart,</l>
<l>being a demon to the demoness who gave [her] breast [to him], who are you, going,</l>
<l>although you know well [his] flesh, having tasted [his] sweet ornaments,</l>
<l>looking out to stretch [your] hand into the hungry mouth of the serpent that is evil deed?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
